{"goals": [{"id": "string", "description": "string", "priority": "high|medium|low"}], "cognitive_mode": "string", "thoughts": ["string"]}

Respond ONLY with the JSON object, no other text.

Respond with valid JSON matching this schema:
{"status": "active|idle|thinking", "thoughts": ["string"], "actions": [], "new_goals": []}

