Respond with valid JSON:
{"goals": [], "thoughts": ["string"], "actions": [], "cognitive_mode": "string"}

Even in an empty state, include at least one thought. Respond ONLY with JSON.

Respond with valid JSON:
{"categories": {"facts": [{"key": "string", "value": "string", "confidence": 0.0}], "observations": ["string"], "questions": ["string"]}, "total_entries": 0, "staleness_score": 0.0}

